# GitHub App Installer (this repo)

**Product name:** GitHub App Installer (not “Claude Token Saver” in user-facing text).

**PyInstaller output:** `dist/GitHubAppInstaller/GitHubAppInstaller.exe`

**After `py -3 build_exe.py`:** the same folder is also copied to **`Desktop/GitHubAppInstaller/`** (Windows, via `Path.home() / "Desktop"`).

**When the user asks to open or run the exe:** use `scripts/open_github_app_installer.ps1` or `scripts/open_github_app_installer.cmd`, or start either path above. If missing, run `build_exe.py` from the repo root.

**Dev (no build):** `py -3 -m claude_backend.gui`

**Legacy names:** `ClaudeTokenSaver`, `launch_token_saver.py`, and `ClaudeTokenSaver.spec` were renamed to `GitHubAppInstaller` / `launch_github_app_installer.py` / `GitHubAppInstaller.spec`.
